<p>Diddy's late mentor: Sadly, the New Jack Swing pioneer (L) died, age 59, from heart failure at his West Hollywood home on May 7 (pictured in 2007)</p>

<p>Sadly, the New Jack Swing pioneer (and Diddy mentor) died, age 59, from heart failure at his West Hollywood home on May 7.</p>

<p>Blige currently plays Monet Stewart Tejada in the 10-episode Power spin-off Power Book II: Ghost, which airs Sundays on Starz.</p>

<p>The two-time Oscar nominee will also portray Grammy winner Dinah Washington in Liesl Tommy's fully-authorized Aretha Franklin biopic Respect, which hits US theaters January 15 and UK theaters January 22.</p>

